Clean node layout for easy customization

Just drag & drop into ComfyUI.

üß© How to Use

Download the JSON workflows from this repo.

Drag them directly into ComfyUI.

Load your input image.

Adjust:

denoise strength

upscale size

prompt (optional)

Render.

Both workflows are designed to work immediately without extra tuning.

‚öôÔ∏è Recommended Settings
Flux DyPE

Denoise: 0.20‚Äì0.35

Tile size: 1024‚Äì1536

Best after a light pre-upscale or SDXL refinement

SRPO Skin Detailer

Denoise: 0.10‚Äì0.20

Avoid over-sharpening

Use mask control for selective skin detail

üìå Notes for Best Results

Don‚Äôt apply both models to the entire image at once.

For portraits:

Use SRPO for skin

Use Flux DyPE for clothing, hair, background

Keep sharpening subtle ‚Äî realism comes from balance, not maximum sharpness.

Avoid 8x upscales in a single pass. Use 2x or 4x chained for stability.

